flowchart TD
    A[Problem Definition] --> B{Cross-Functional<br/>Input?}
    B -->|Yes| C[Shared Problem Framing]
    B -->|No| D[Data-Driven Framing Only]
    D --> E[Risk: Technically Elegant<br/>but Misaligned Solution]
    C --> F[Data Acquisition<br/>and Preparation]
    F --> G[Model Development<br/>with Shared Visibility]
    G --> H{Legal and Compliance<br/>Review}
    H -->|Approved| I[Cross-Functional<br/>Deployment Checkpoint]
    H -->|Issues Found| J[Iterate with<br/>Feedback Loop]
    J --> G
    I --> K[Operational Monitoring<br/>as Cross-Functional Loop]
    K --> L{Performance<br/>Drift Detected?}
    L -->|Yes| M[Business, Data, and Legal<br/>Joint Response]
    M --> G
    L -->|No| N[Continuous Stakeholder<br/>Feedback]
    N --> K